    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK130">
<l>kataṅkāttuk kaṟṟaṭaṅka lāṟṟuvāṉ cevvi</l>
<l>yaṟampārkku māṟṟi ṉuḻaintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the learned man who, guarding against wrath, controls himself, dharma</l>
<l>will look for any opportunity, following his path.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
